4.2 Market barriers In the remainder of this paper we focus on the effect of various forms of market barriers on the ability of a system of agents to reach a state of acceptable satisfaction.
Secondly, the  relatively higher market share enjoyed by market leaders in highly-connected networks is eroded by market barriers.
